OL,4,CAre we taming offshore finance?
OL,5, The offshore finance industry puts
OL,6, trillions of dollars worldwide beyond
OL,7, the taxman's reach. Bringing it to heel
OL,8, is like taming a cat; not just a normal
OL,9, moggy - a thankless task in itself -
OL,10, but a Cheshire Cat: nebulous, hard to
OL,11, pin down, disappearing and reappearing
OL,12, when it likes.
OL,16,FOne adage cited by the taxation author
OL,17,Fand expert Nicholas Shaxson sums it up:
OL,18,F"Those who know don't talk. And those
OL,19,Fwho talk don't know." 
